:: Wolfgang watches as his young apprentice fires at the decepticon
warrrior.  As Wolfgang sees Masabot's bravery and courage, he starts to
realise that he can stand on his own two feet.  He decides to head back to
base, but knowing Masabot's inexpierence, he decides to make contact. ::

*Speaks into his com-link*"Masabot, if you need help in any way, contact me
immediatly."*

:: Starts his jet packs and heads back to base. ::
